ds-edit-subheading: Uma ungasafuni ukuthi izikhungo zikhunjulwe kule divayisi, sisuse ohlwini olungezansi.
ds-notice-and-consent-banner-storage-inf: Isikhungo ozama ukusikhetha sizolondolozwa  kusitoreji sasendaweni sale bhrawuza futhi sizokwenziwa sitholakale kule sayithi kanye namanye asebenzisa Ukufinyelela Okulula. Ungakwazi ukusula isitoreji sasendaweni sebhrawuza yakho nganom yisiphi isikhathi.
ds-notice-and-consent-banner-personal-in: Akukho ukungena ngemvume, i-imeyili noma ulwazi lomuntu siqu olugcinwayo.
